public void getPresenter(NotifyingAsyncCallback<P> callback)
Description copied from interface: Proxy
Get the associated Presenter. The presenter can only be obtained in an asynchronous manner to support code splitting when needed. To access the presenter, pass a callback.

getRawPresenter

public void getRawPresenter(NotifyingAsyncCallback<Presenter<?,?>> callback)
Description copied from interface: ProxyRaw
Get the associated Presenter. The presenter can only be obtained in an asynchronous manner to support code splitting when needed. To access the presenter, pass a callback.

The difference between this method and Proxy.getPresenter(com.gwtplatform.mvp.client.proxy.NotifyingAsyncCallback

) is that the latter one gets the specific parameterised Presenter type.

bind

@Inject
protected void bind(PlaceManager placeManager,
                           EventBus eventBus)
Injects the various resources and performs other bindings.

Never call directly, it should only be called by GIN. Method injection is used instead of constructor injection, because the latter doesn't work well with GWT generators.

Parameters:
placeManager - The PlaceManager. Ignored.
eventBus - The EventBus.
